<h1><span lang="EN-AU">Custom metric integration
to the COSO Data Lake for OpsBridge reporting solutions<o:p></o:p></span></h1>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-AU">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-AU">This
section describes how to extend the COSO Data Lake to collect custom metrics to
enable custom reporting using Business Value Dashboard or your own BI reporting
tools.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-AU">This
section covers the following topics:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:
