following diagram shows the components used in collecting custom metrics.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-AU"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-AU"><img src="https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/PN/diag1.png"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-AU"><br></span></p>